text: Dezső is a Hungarian given male name, the Hungarian form of Desiderius. It may refer to: ==People== *Dezsö, French DJ* *Dezso_the_best, streamer youtubos *Dezső Bánffy, Hungarian politician *Dezső Ernster, Hungarian opera singer *Dezső Földes, Hungarian 2x Olympic champion saber fencer *Dezső Kanizsai, Hungarian audiologist *Dezső Kosztolányi, Hungarian poet and writer * Dezső Ránki, Hungarian concert pianist *Dezső Vaghy, Hungarian violinist (of the Vaghy String Quartet) ==See also== *3892 Dezsö, a main belt asteroid Category:Hungarian masculine given names
title: Dezső
